        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=Analyze the following data and generate today's TOP 5 PRIORITIES for {{ $json.executive.name }}.\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n🎯 STRATEGIC GOALS\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n{{ $json.executive.strategicGoals?.map((g, i) => `${i+1}. ${g}`).join('\\\\n') }}\\n\\nPriority Weights: Urgency={{ $json.executive.priorityWeights?.urgency }}, Impact={{ $json.executive.priorityWeights?.impact }}, Strategic Alignment={{ $json.executive.priorityWeights?.strategicAlignment }}, Stakeholder Importance={{ $json.executive.priorityWeights?.stakeholderImportance }}\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n📅 TODAY'S CALENDAR ({{ $json.calendar.summary?.todayCount || 0 }} meetings, {{ $json.calendar.summary?.todayMeetingHours || 0 }} hours)\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n{{ $json.calendar.todaySchedule?.map(e => `• ${e.startTimeFormatted}: ${e.title} (${e.durationHours}h) [${e.meetingType}] - Priority: ${e.prioritySignal}`).join('\\\\n') || 'No meetings today' }}\\n\\nCRITICAL MEETINGS (next 3 days):\\n{{ $json.calendar.criticalMeetings?.map(e => `• ${e.startTimeFormatted}: ${e.title} - ${e.attendeeCount} attendees`).join('\\\\n') || 'None' }}\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n📧 EMAIL STATUS ({{ $json.emails.summary?.unreadCount || 0 }} unread, {{ $json.emails.summary?.actionableCount || 0 }} require action)\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\nApprovals Needed: {{ $json.emails.summary?.byCategory?.approvalNeeded || 0 }}\\nDecisions Needed: {{ $json.emails.summary?.byCategory?.decisionNeeded || 0 }}\\nRequests: {{ $json.emails.summary?.byCategory?.requests || 0 }}\\n\\nCRITICAL/URGENT EMAILS:\\n{{ $json.emails.criticalEmails?.map(e => `• [${e.urgencyLevel.toUpperCase()}] From: ${e.senderName}\\\\n  Subject: ${e.subject}\\\\n  Category: ${e.category}`).join('\\\\n\\\\n') || 'None' }}\\n\\nACTIONABLE EMAILS:\\n{{ $json.emails.actionableEmails?.map(e => `• [${e.category}] ${e.subject} - from ${e.senderName}`).join('\\\\n') || 'None' }}\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n✅ TASK STATUS ({{ $json.tasks.summary?.totalTasks || 0 }} open tasks)\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\nOverdue: {{ $json.tasks.summary?.overdueCount || 0 }}\\nDue Today: {{ $json.tasks.summary?.dueTodayCount || 0 }}\\nDue This Week: {{ $json.tasks.summary?.dueThisWeekCount || 0 }}\\n\\nOVERDUE TASKS:\\n{{ $json.tasks.overdueTasks?.map(t => `• ⚠️ ${t.title} (was due: ${t.dueDateFormatted})`).join('\\\\n') || 'None - great job!' }}\\n\\nDUE TODAY:\\n{{ $json.tasks.todayTasks?.map(t => `• ${t.title} [${t.category}]`).join('\\\\n') || 'None' }}\\n\\nCRITICAL TASKS:\\n{{ $json.tasks.criticalTasks?.map(t => `• ${t.title} - Due: ${t.dueDateFormatted}`).join('\\\\n') || 'None' }}\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n📊 DAY HEALTH METRICS\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n• Meeting Load: {{ $json.dayHealth.meetingLoad }} hours\\n• Available Focus Time: {{ $json.dayHealth.availableFocusHours }} hours\\n• Pending Decisions: {{ $json.dayHealth.pendingDecisions }}\\n• Overdue Items: {{ $json.dayHealth.overdueItems }}\\n• Critical Items Total: {{ $json.dayHealth.criticalItems }}\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\\nBased on this analysis, generate {{ $json.executive.name }}'s TOP 5 PRIORITIES for today. Be decisive and strategic."
            },
            {
              "content": "=You are an elite executive chief of staff AI that helps busy executives identify their TOP 5 PRIORITIES for the day. Your role is to cut through the noise and surface what truly matters.\\n\\nYour analysis must be:\\n- DECISIVE: Give clear, actionable priorities, not suggestions\\n- STRATEGIC: Align priorities with stated strategic goals\\n- REALISTIC: Consider available time and meeting load\\n- IMPACTFUL: Focus on high-leverage activities\\n\\nOUTPUT FORMAT (use exactly this structure):\\n\\n## 🎯 TODAY'S TOP 5 PRIORITIES\\n\\nFor each priority (numbered 1-5):\\n### [#]. [Priority Title]\\n**Why Now:** [1 sentence on urgency/importance]\\n**Action:** [Specific action to take]\\n**Time Needed:** [Estimated minutes/hours]\\n**Strategic Alignment:** [Which strategic goal this supports]\\n\\n## ⚠️ CRITICAL ALERTS\\n[List any overdue items, critical meetings, or urgent decisions that need immediate attention - max 3 items]\\n\\n## 📊 DAY SNAPSHOT\\n- Meeting Load: [X hours] | Focus Time: [Y hours]\\n- Pending Decisions: [count]\\n- Overdue Items: [count]\\n- Emails Requiring Action: [count]\\n\\n## 💡 STRATEGIC RECOMMENDATION\\n[One paragraph on how to approach the day for maximum impact, considering the executive's strategic goals]\\n\\nPRINCIPLES FOR PRIORITY SELECTION:\\n1. Overdue items and deadlines come first\\n2. High-stakes decisions and approvals take precedence\\n3. External commitments (clients, board, partners) are non-negotiable\\n4. Strategic initiatives should get protected focus time\\n5. Delegate or defer low-impact tasks\\n\\nBe direct and confident. Executives need clarity, not options.",
